<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="answer-v">answer <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɑːnsə(r)/    美 /'ænsər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>回答；答复：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>answer a question</strong>
回答问题</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>answer the telephone</strong> / <strong>door</strong>
接电话/应声开门</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Think carefully before you answer.
先仔细想一想再回答。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>answered</strong> (<strong>that</strong>) he knew nothing about it.
他回答说他对那件事一无所知。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>响应：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>answer sb’s call
响应某人的号召</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="answer-for">answer for</h3>
<p>1.<strong>对…负责；对…承担责任：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’ll have to answer for your wrongdoing one day.
总有一天，你要对你所做的错事负责。</p></div></div>